    {\displaystyle (2k+1)2^{n}.}
   The Bernoulli polynomials are recovered by setting 
  
    
      
        k
        =
        0
      
    
    {\displaystyle k=0}
   and 
  
    
      
        z
        =
        
          
            1
            2
          
        
        ,
        
          
            1
            4
          
        
