    {\displaystyle Z=\sum _{\{\sigma _{i}=\pm 1,\,i\in \mathbb {Z} _{N}\}}\prod _{i\in \mathbb {Z} _{N}}{\mathcal {R}}[C]e^{-{\mathcal {R}}[\beta g]\sigma _{i}\sigma _{i+1}},}
  provided we replace 
  
    
      
        C
      
    
